{"type": "root", "attrs": {"icon": "FUR/isolate_parts", "parent": "hairtools"}, "body": [{"level": 0, "type": "title", "indent": 0, "text": ["Isolate Groom Parts"], "extent": [45, 69]}, {"type": "summary", "indent": 0, "text": ["Hide and disable unselected parts of a groom for faster feedback."], "extent": [69, 143]}, {"level": 2, "id": null, "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 0, "text": ["Overview"], "extent": [143, 158], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["This tool allows you to hide ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/obj/hairgen", "type": "link", "text": ["Hair Generate"], "fullpath": "/nodes/obj/hairgen"}, " objects that don\u2019t operate on the same region as selected ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/obj/guidegroom", "type": "link", "text": ["Guide Groom"], "fullpath": "/nodes/obj/guidegroom"}, " nodes. It also fills in the ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Isolate Groom Objects"]}, " parameter in any ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/obj/groommerge", "type": "link", "text": ["Groom Merge"], "fullpath": "/nodes/obj/groommerge"}, " that references the selected nodes, causing these to ignore any other nodes. Running the tool with all relevant ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/obj/guidegroom", "type": "link", "text": ["Guide Groom"], "fullpath": "/nodes/obj/guidegroom"}, " selected clears the parameter."], "extent": [158, 596]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["This tool is useful for speeding up cooking and for getting a clear view of the area you're currently working on."], "extent": [596, 711]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["For more information, see the ", {"scheme": null, "value": "/fur/workflow", "type": "link", "text": ["Fur Workflow"], "fullpath": "/fur/workflow"}, " help."], "extent": [711, 777]}]}, {"level": 2, "id": "includeme", "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 0, "text": ["Using Isolate Groom Parts"], "extent": [777, 821], "body": [{"type": "ord_group", "body": [{"blevel": 6, "type": "ord", "indent": 4, "text": ["Select the ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/obj/guidegroom", "type": "link", "text": ["Guide Groom"], "fullpath": "/nodes/obj/guidegroom"}, " you want to work on."], "extent": [821, 895]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "ord", "indent": 4, "text": ["Click the ", {"scheme": "Icon", "value": "FUR/isolate_parts", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/shelf/FUR/isolate_parts"}, {"type": "ui", "text": ["Isolate Groom Parts"]}, " tool on the ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Hair Utils"]}, " tab. This will hide the ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/obj/hairgen", "type": "link", "text": ["Hair Generate"], "fullpath": "/nodes/obj/hairgen"}, " objects that don\u2019t use the selected guides."], "extent": [895, 1092]}], "container": true}, {"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": [{"scheme": "Image", "value": "/images/fur/isolate.jpg", "type": "img", "text": ""}], "extent": [1092, 1133]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["This example shows fur being generated on the head, but not the torso, since only the head was selected before using this tool."], "extent": [1133, 1270]}, {"type": "tip_group", "body": [{"type": "tip", "indent": 4, "role": "item", "extent": [1270, 1279], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["If you select another ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/obj/guidegroom", "type": "link", "text": ["Guide Groom"], "fullpath": "/nodes/obj/guidegroom"}, " section to work on and use this tool, it will hide the previous one and only display the newly selected one."], "extent": [1279, 1462]}], "container": true}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}]}], "title": ["Isolate Groom Parts"], "summary": ["Hide and disable unselected parts of a groom for faster feedback."]}